704065f-b.title: Brooklyn: New York Avenue (East) - Atlantic Avenue
704065f-b.text:

background the Junction for all B.M.T. Elevated lines in this area.
May 1929.

704063f-a.title: Brooklyn: New York Avenue (East) - Atlantic Avenue
704063f-a.text:
East New York Ave., north side, between Atlantic Ave., and Pacific
Street. In the background is the East New York Station of the Long
Island Railroad.
July 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
